Who's coming? Our very special event is just over a week away. 
This isn't your usual exhibition. This is an event. An intimate unfolding. A chance to see and be seen. 
These artists have been digging deep, creating, confronting and finding their truth so that you can find your own... The event is called She Spoke for a reason. The more that we find, and give voice to our own truths, the more we can encourage others to do the same. 
The evening will be unexpected and unprecedented.

Grab your ticket and join us! You will be our special guest and well taken care of! 
www.becomingartists.org

xx jessica

When you smile, I just think. If I am the only reason of that. You are never need me to be more colorful, because you have a lot of colors which can make another people around you to be happy. You are like a ghost who always live near me. You have been here and I can't hug and catch you. You are like a rain around me and I hindered by clouds above my head. I just a low person who can't love you as much as I want. Because I just the one who do not never loved by you. There is no one who can change you in my heart. Although My tears always flow, I want to see you again and again. I feel that you are always here, in my heart. Although I never find you, never see you, and never touch you.  Complete life when I could keep your hand in my hand too, but It's just a dream because you never need me. So, I just keep you deep in my heart and no one could see you there.
.
